rows.label: tlk42300042_01_msg0001
rows.name: Are there red barrels in the city, mo?

rows.label: tlk42300042_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Those are barrels handled by the Nopon
trade guilds, mo. They're painted red
to make them easy to identify, mo.

rows.label: tlk42300042_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Other guilds besides Avaritia
use them too, they're common
nationwide, mo.

rows.label: tlk42300042_01_msg0004
rows.name: And sometimes we lock them, mo.

rows.label: tlk42300042_01_msg0005
rows.name:
But recently, some people have
been breaking them, which is
a bit of a problem, mo.
